A python tcp server / client library use socket and select,
single thread, can use with gobject.timeout_add.

public method:

class ServerSocket:
	def get_active_client(self)
	def close(self)

class Socket:
	def close(self)
	def wait(self)
	def has_data(self)
	def get_data(self)

def create_server(bind_port, bind_address="0.0.0.0")
def create_connection(address)
def close_server(bind_port, bind_address="0.0.0.0")
def get_active_client(lst=None)
def handle()